skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: museum voice
des: A great skill for museum lovers in the UK! Ask museum voice for your daily update on cultural events in your city. Discover inspirational exhibitions, kids’ programs, museum workshops and much more. Every day you get three ideas for events to attend near where you're based. We are working in partnership with Culture24 to provide the most up-to-date and accurate information. Do you have suggestions and ideas to make the skill better? Please contact us at info@museotechniki.com. (version 1.0.0)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
